Text: This week we began by selecting the projects we were going to be working on for the next few weeks, I got sorted into the groups working on the Cook Brothers project.
2 days after that we got together with our project leader Loic, and went through what he wanted out of our group.
Overall everything is working out ok, we have a general idea of how everything is going to work and the process of how we are going to carry it out.
However i feel like i am definitely the weakest link, my organisation seems to be weighing down the team in terms of communication.
I will try to get on top of this.
We have another meeting with Loic the next week where hes going to go through each of the different languages and interfaces we will be working with.
While i haven't learnt anything as of now, i am very interested and intrigued at the prospect of learning and working with a professional.
